                            .text("The alternative assets industry has exhibited remarkable growth in recent years, firmly establishing itself as a cornerstone of the modern investment landscape. Notably, the total assets under management within this sector have reached historic highs, underscoring its ever-increasing importance. (19) "),
                            .text("Furthermore, the appeal of alternative investments has been steadily on the rise, with both investors and fund managers expressing sustained and expanding interest in this diverse field. This upsurge reflects the industry's adaptability, capacity for innovation, and its ability to offer investors unique opportunities that extend beyond traditional investment avenues."),
