                    Section(
                        id: "sec_mod_gender_2",
                        title: "💬 Overcoming the Great Barrier: Yourself_",
                        content: [
                            .text("One of the greatest factors that you need to understand in any sort of investing is Autonomy. Historically financial products were with a “one size fits all” approach, if you did not fit that size then the problem laid with you. In actuality the issue lies within the biases that laid the groundwork for the architecture of the financial products themselves. "),
                            .callout(title: "Wealth Perspective", content: "One of the highest forms of Wealth is the ability to know that you are building the life you desire, have the financial flexibly to wake up morning, stretch, say to yourself, \"I can do whatever I want today.\"- adapted from the Psychology of Money", type: .info)
                        ],
                        isCollapsible: true,
                        level: 2,
